title: Amazon Brings Its One-Hour Delivery Service, Prime Now, To The San Francisco Bay Area
text: Amazon this morning announced it’s expanding its one-hour delivery service, Prime Now, to two more markets: the San Francisco Bay Area and San Antonio, Texas. The company had clearly been ramping up operations in California, in preparation to serve the Bay Area and beyond, as it currently has five fulfillment centers in the state, employing over 10,000 individuals in full-time positions.… Read More »
